@staff_access_token=YOUR_STAFF_TOKEN_HERE
@order_id=YOUR_ORDER_ID_HERE

### Get New Orders (Staff)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/orders?status=NEW&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{staff_access_token}}

### Confirm Order (Staff)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/orders/{{order_id}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{staff_access_token}}

### Start Preparing Order (Kitchen/Staff)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/orders/{{order_id}}/prepare
Authorization: Bearer {{staff_access_token}}

### Update Status to Ready (Generic)
PATCH http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/orders/{{order_id}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{staff_access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "READY"
}

### Update Status to Completed (Generic)
PATCH http://localhost:5001/api/v1/internal/orders/{{order_id}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{staff_access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "COMPLETED"
}
